org.janelia.flyem.neuprint

Class NeuPrintMain

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.janelia.flyem.neuprint.NeuPrintMain

  • public class NeuPrintMain
extends java.lang.Object
    The NeuPrintMain class implements an application that loads neuron and synapse data provided by JSON files into a neo4j database.
    See Also:
    neuron, synapse, and connections JSON spec
